      </div>

      <h2 class="lp-features-heading" id="features2-heading" data-i18n-html="s02.heading">
        Your entire knowledge base,<br /><em>always at hand</em>.
      </h2>

      <div class="lp-feat-grid lp-feat-grid-split">
