              >
            </div>
            <h3 data-i18n="s02.c1.h3">Markdown-first editing</h3>
            <p data-i18n="s02.c1.p">
              Write the way your brain works. kuku understands structure and surfaces it
              intelligently.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="lp-feat-viz">
            <div class="lp-fv lp-fv-md lp-fv-md-editor" id="lp-demo-md">
